**[Scopes](https://developers.zoom.us/docs/integrations/oauth-scopes-overview/):** `group:write:admin`

**[Granular Scopes](https://developers.zoom.us/docs/integrations/oauth-scopes-overview/):** `group:update:registration_settings:admin`

**[Rate Limit Label](https://marketplace.zoom.us/docs/api-reference/rate-limits#rate-limits):** `MEDIUM`

